## 5. Domain Entities

| Entity           | Description                                              |
|------------------|----------------------------------------------------------|
| `Generic`        | Drug active ingredient (`name`, `arabic_name`)           |
| `Brand`          | Commercial product → linked to Generic, Manufacturer, DosageForm |
| `Manufacturer`   | Pharmaceutical company (`country`, `website`)            |
| `DosageForm`     | Drug form (tablet, syrup, injection, …)                  |
| `TherapeuticClass` | ATC hierarchy (parent-child, `level`, `code`)          |
| `Price`          | Drug pricing in IQD → linked to Brand                    |
| `Alternative`    | Drug substitutes → linked to Generic                     |

