## 6. Testing Guidelines

- Backend tests: `tests/` (pytest)
  - Unit: `tests/unit/` — services, repositories
  - Integration: `tests/integration/` — API endpoints
- Shared fixtures in `conftest.py`
- Mock all external dependencies; test business logic in isolation
- Run suite: `pytest` from project root

