## 8. Token Optimization

- Read only the files required to complete the task
- Prefer targeted `edit` calls over full-file rewrites
- Use `@file.ts:10-20` line-range syntax for precise reads
- Skip `venv/`, `node_modules/`, `__pycache__/`, `.git/`
- Debug path: `models/ → repositories/ → services/ → endpoints/`
- Frontend debug path: component → its types → its service module
- Always run `grep`/`code_search` before opening files

